r quality. To ensure food security and environmental sustainability, it is necessary to implement proper manure management practices on cropland across the globe. Datasets are available at {$<$}a href="https://doi.org/10.1594/PANGAEA.871980" target="\_blank"{$>$}https://doi.org/10.1594/PANGAEA.871980{$<$}/a{$>$} (Zhang et al., 2017).{$<$}/p{$>$}},
